        <qualifiedname>bt_cap_unicast_audio_start_stream_param::codec_cfg</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Codec configuration. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The <computeroutput>codec_cfg.meta</computeroutput> shall include a list of CCIDs (<ref refid="group__bt__assigned__numbers__audio_1ggab53d0dd62bceff97cf8eed7d8cf80354a37b5552e04734392dc6c6eb9e19b377b" kindref="member">BT_AUDIO_METADATA_TYPE_CCID_LIST</ref>) as well as a non-0 stream context (<ref refid="group__bt__assigned__numbers__audio_1ggab53d0dd62bceff97cf8eed7d8cf80354a95f128b11584ee22100ae65ce751dbaa" kindref="member">BT_AUDIO_METADATA_TYPE_STREAM_CONTEXT</ref>) bitfield.</para>
<para>This value is assigned to the <computeroutput>stream</computeroutput>, and shall remain valid while the stream is non-idle. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
